high_descs: Walk a few steps forward, hang a right, then make a left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the spoon that is in the sink.
Place the spoon in the mug that is also in the kitchen sink.
Pick up the mug with the spoon in it.
Move towards your right a bit to the counter space.
Sit the mug with the spoon down on the counter in front of and to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Move a mug and spoon from the sink to the counter.

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up the spoon that is in the sink.
Place the spoon in the cup that is in the sink.
Pick the cup up with the spoon in it that is in the sink.
With the spoon in the cup turn and go to where the toaster is on the counter.
Place the cup in front of the toaster to the left near the edge of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put spoon and cup on counter.

high_descs: turn right, walk to the sink on the left
grab the spoon in the sink
put the spoon in the cup in the sink
take the cup from the sink
walk to the right a little to the counter
put the cup on the counter
anns.task_desc: put the spoon in the cup in the sink, move the cup to the counter
